---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<aside class="subscribe">
	<div class="label">/ stay-in-touch</div>
	<p class="lede">如果这篇文章对你有用,留个入口下次还能找到我。</p>
	<ul class="links">
		<li>
			<span class="key">rss</span>
			<a href={base + '/rss.xml'}>订阅 feed</a>
			<span class="hint">— 喂给 Reeder / Feedly / Inoreader</span>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="key">github</span>
			<a href="https://github.com/yli769227-jpg/ai-thoughts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">star · watch this repo</a>
			<span class="hint">— 新文章会作为 commit 推送,Watch 后第一时间收到通知</span>
		</li>
		<li>
			<span class="key">author</span>
			<a href="https://github.com/yli769227-jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">follow @yli769227-jpg</a>
			<span class="hint">— 关注作者本人</span>
		</li>
	</ul>
</aside>

<style>
	.subscribe {
		margin: 3em 0 2em;
		padding: 1.6em 1.8em;
		border: 1px solid var(--silver);
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(41, 72, 255, 0.025), transparent);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}
	.label {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.72em;
		color: var(--accent);
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 0.7em;
	}
	.lede {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 1.1em;
		color: var(--ink);
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin: 0 0 1.2em;
	}
	.links {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.84em;
		line-height: 1.85;
	}
	.links li {
		margin: 0.15em 0;
		color: var(--slate);
	}
	.key {
		display: inline-block;
		min-width: 4.2em;
		color: var(--accent);
		opacity: 0.7;
	}
	.key::before {
		content: '→ ';
	}
	.links a {
		color: var(--ink);
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
		transition: border-color var(--transition), color var(--transition);
	}
	.links a:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
		border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
	}
	.hint {
		color: var(--slate);
		opacity: 0.85;
	}
	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.subscribe {
			padding: 1.2em 1.2em;
		}
		.key {
			display: block;
			min-width: 0;
			margin-top: 0.4em;
		}
		.hint {
			display: block;
			padding-left: 0;
			font-size: 0.92em;
		}
	}
</style>
